Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trebor1號呼叫飛龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是飛龍  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西北方向出現大型移動物體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大型移動物體？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法通過IRUO.進行情報搜索操作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推測其長度超過15米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照預定計劃  Trebor繼續原地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,專心準備發射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離發射還有47分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,液體燃料準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風速1.0  無降水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大型移動物體即將抵達發射場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,申請發射導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛龍呼叫Trebor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否使用導彈由我來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要離開工作崗位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美紗姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(212,290)\fad(500,500)\3cD99437\blur4\b1}#22「接下來的遊戲是屬於我們的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AR誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟動！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這就是戰場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  真不愧是澤田親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來AR誘餌好像起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導彈無效的話就沒什麼好怕的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣逼近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  並不是所有的導彈都被無效化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AR誘餌通過干擾IRUO.  來使對方將AR誤認為本體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使其難以擊中本體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是類似於分身術一般的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然幾率很低
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是有可能偶然命中本體的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希  按下按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打樁機…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右手的還能用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要跑嗎  美紗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SUMERAGI正與大型移動物體交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續進行發射倒計時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一有破綻我就衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩30分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離這麼近的話  你就沒法發射導彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  美紗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那機體可是我進行調整的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怒吼吧！磁單極子驅動器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel十字火箭拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒它了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的攝像機應該已經被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美紗姐  你聽得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來向小亞希…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親口向小亞希解釋一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼放棄了Gun製造計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要說出那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你全都要給我解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了聽你的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希一路追了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並追上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逃避啊  美紗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾  你遲了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的意識已經崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我將其沉入了黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自爆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是個沒有自我意識的牽線木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而操縱她的人正是我君島晃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君島…晃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是B小組
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已成功奪回控制室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來開始停止火箭發射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭的發射是不會停下的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我必須要讓實驗成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚…嗚哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死了  真的死了  剛剛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但接下來只能靠內部電池了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運轉時間大約為5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希穗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管嘗試多少次  火箭都不接受發射中止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令被管理員攔截了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的管理員是…君島晃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼哼  這實驗可是賭上了這麼長的時間和我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要讓它成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來來…來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澤田親  ktkr
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神代同學  這時候還是別開玩笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程序發過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠刪除掉君島晃的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要使用的話  需先進行安裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後讓君島的AR出現在口袋本的畫面上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並將其鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安裝需要重啟口袋本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重啟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後還要想盡辦法把姐姐從駕駛艙裏弄出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話就一定能捕捉到君島晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩10分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信完全切斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是在做些什麼小動作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒反應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部長  八汐學長正在重啟口袋本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他完全看不到對方的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是亞希啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說她居然還有自我意識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希  快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊  美紗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊  放馬過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美紗姐你應該不是那種會在電視上點頭哈腰的和藹類型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而應該是能夠若無其事地取得完全勝利的無情女人  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明是個女孩子  卻喜歡機器人動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種鄉下居然還真心想著要造什麼巨型機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後還把周圍的人全都拉下水  你不是這種笨女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(439,325)\fs16}Right Stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的你  還有只屬於自己的正確資質嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我啊  美紗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是再這麼大放厥詞的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就滅了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  接下來的遊戲是屬於我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是知道的  美紗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你玩「Kiilballad」的時候也總是這樣出招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對美紗姐  我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往右躲四幀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很遺憾  但美紗希已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是Gun製造1號機哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐你曾經一直在製造的機器人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這裏就是為了說這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是凝聚了姐姐和我還有大家的思念的機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它正打算去拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你們姐妹倆都有驚人的精神力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他第一次給我看機器人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我喜歡機器人！  喜歡它勝過這世上的一切！」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在  你還喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你現在還喜歡機器人勝過這世上的一切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明  明明就只差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過總有一天  還會有第二個  第三個我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  就算這樣正義似乎還是總會取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的部長是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許她說的對…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已從君島晃手上取得了管理員權限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸入停止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒計時停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們成功阻止了火箭的發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來…來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝擊力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波霸～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  這搖滾還真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美紗姐情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是暈過去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海  我們回機庫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海你今後有什麼打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後是指？
